		<p>The first time we tricked our brains like that was over <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/History_of_animation#Early_approaches_to_motion_in_art">5,000 years ago</a>. We never stopped since. Animation has been with us through time as we told stories and brought them to life through sound, written word, and images.</p>
